<h1>The Quest</h1>
<p style="margin-top:20px;">There’s a scene in the movie, Ratatouille, where Anton Ego, the critical food critic, takes a bite of the titular dish. He is instantly transported to his childhood. There is something about being in that moment. It’s a moment I seek. The rest of world disappears. I can no longer hear. I can no longer see. All I can do is taste. And it is pure pleasure. </p>

<p>This journey will take me around the world, to visit 50 of the <a href="https://www.theworlds50best.com">World’s Best Restaurants</a>. I am no food critic. I have no sway. I’m just a guy who enjoys really good food and enjoys to travel. </p>

<p>I have a Google Spreadsheet <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1NPckHqoxjhqoUIzrI2KSzU1AWeettEVEsykZYgUyd9w/edit?usp=sharing">list of all the restaurants</a>. Each year, a new list will come out and I will update this spreadsheet. What you’ll find on this site is a history of all the places I’ve been. </p>

<p>Enjoy!</p>



